# <type>(<scope>): <subject>   (<=72 chars, imperative, no trailing period)
#
# <body: what & why, wrap at 72>
#
# <footer: BREAKING CHANGE: ... / Refs: ...>
#
# Conventional Commits 1.0.0 — types:
#   feat     a new feature
#   fix      a bug fix
#   docs     documentation only
#   test     adding/correcting tests
#   refactor neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
#   perf     performance improvement
#   build    build system / deps
#   ci       CI configuration
#   chore    other (no src or test change)
#   security a security-relevant change (fix/hardening)
#
# scopes (this repo): teap, eap-core, fips-tls, creds, pac, eaphost,
#                     eaphost-config, cli, kat, workspace, docs
